Barbara Johnson, Trial Court Coordinator.

Robert B. Williams, for Williams, Robert B. Susan I. Doyle, District Attorney, for State of North Carolina.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 10th of July 2019 by Defendant for Notice of Appeal of a Writ of Habeas Corpus in State Court:
